* upload pictures
Unable to create directory wp-content/uploads/2018/11. Is its parent directory writable by the server?

chmod 777 /var/www/html/wp-content


* alter the footer
wp-content/themes/<your-theme>/footer.php


* post not found error(why?)
alter the /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf
load rewrite module

LoadModule rewrite_module modules/mod_rewrite.so

AllowOverride all

* ftp connection
add the following content into wp-config.php 

define("FS_METHOD","direct");
define("FS_CHMOD_DIR", 0777);
define("FS_CHMOD_FILE", 0777);


chmod 777 wp-themes wp-plugins


